riday, purifies himself as much as he can, uses oil or perfume in his house, then proceeds for prayer and does not separate two persons sitting together, then prays as much as\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25289,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/22\/increase-dua-prophet-jumuah\/","url_meta":{"origin":28427,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Supplications for the Prophet on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIncrease your supplications for me on the day and night of Friday. Whoever blesses me once, Allah will bless him ten times.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 5994 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15807,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/wudu-friday-ghusl-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":28427,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Recommendation to bathe on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah ibn Jundab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs ablution on Friday has done well, but whoe